      • setBank

        public double setBank(SkyowalletBank bank)
        Sets the bank of the account. null if you want to clear the account's bank.
        The player's wallet will be set to the current wallet + its bank balance. The bank balance will be set to 0.
        Parameters:
        bank - The bank. null if you want to clear the account's bank.
        Returns:
        The old bank balance.

      • setBank

        public double setBank(SkyowalletBank bank,
                      boolean round)
        Sets the bank of the account. null if you want to clear the account's bank.
        The player's wallet will be set to the current wallet + its bank balance. The bank balance will be set to 0.
        Parameters:
        bank - The bank. null if you want to clear the account's bank.
        round - If you want to round the account total wallet.
        Returns:
        The old bank balance.
        -1.0 will be returned if the event is cancelled or if this account is already in the specified bank.
